aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLI_LifeDisabilityRuleEngine) (Def Version:2) (Implem Version:1)
uses WFTypes
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Num8) var returnString : CString var coverageAmount : tWFAmount var currentDate : tWFDate var deathDate : tWFDate var daysBetween : Int4 var indexValue : Num8
coverageAmount = self.Option__CoverageAmount currentDate = self.Real__CurrentDate deathDate = self.Death__DeathDate indexValue = self.Index('BenefitDisbDelayInterest', self.Death__DeathDate) daysBetween = currentDate - deathDate returnString = 'The benefit calculation was calculated using the interest rate of ' returnString = Concat(returnString, indexValue) returnString = Concat(returnString, ' over a period of ') returnString = Concat(returnString, daysBetween) returnString = Concat(returnString, ' day(s) with a coverage amount of ') returnString = Concat(returnString, coverageAmount) Alert(returnString) self.AppendComment(returnString) Result = coverageAmount + coverageAmount * indexValue * daysBetween endProc
aWFRuleDesc.Name: Coverage Amount + Interest
